data.description: Move-in ready! Modern is the key word here. All new carpet, spacious interior featuring high ceilings, LED lighting, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and quality touches through-out. Dark hardwood floors, upgraded vanity with glass vessel sinks in primary ensuite bath. Outside you'll find a privacy fenced backyard, large deck for entertaining, and perimeter lighting.   Eligible for VA assumption at 2.625%
